instructions: put dinner plate in the center of table cloth
put salad plate on top of dinner plate
put napkin on top of salad plate
put wine glass on the right upper corner of table cloth
put water glass on the top right corner of table cloth, right of wine glass
put salad fork on the left of dinner plate
put dinner fork right of salad fork
put dinner knife on the right side of dinner plate
put soup spoon on the right side of dinner knife
